PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of LORE MARIE MIRWALDT, of The Pas, Manitoba, as a director of the board of directors of the Canada Ports Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of six months, in the place of John Ronald Longstaffe, whose term has expired.
